<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Insufficient Word Coins - WorkHub Writers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/default.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/token.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div id="nav-brand">
            <div onclick="location.href='/'">
                <img src="/logo.svg" alt="" id="logo-image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="insufficient-tokens">
        <h1>Insufficient Word Coins</h1>

        <div class="token-alert">
            <div class="alert-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="alert-message">
                <p>You need <strong><%= requiredTokens %> Word Coins (WC)</strong> to apply for this job, but you only have <strong><%= user.tokens %> WC</strong>.</p>
                <p>Purchase more Word Coins to continue with your application.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/token" class="btn primary-btn">Purchase Word Coins</a>
            <a href="/job/id/<%= jobId %>" class="btn secondary-btn">Back to Job</a>
        </div>

        <div class="token-info">
            <h3>Why do I need Word Coins?</h3>
            <p>Word Coins (WC) are used to apply for jobs on WorkHub Writers. Each job application requires a specific number of Word Coins, typically based on the job's complexity and value.</p>
            <p>Word Coins help ensure that only serious applicants apply for jobs, improving the quality of proposals for clients.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <small>WorkHub Writers &copy; <span class="year"></span></small>
    </footer>

    <script>
        document.querySelector('.year').innerHTML = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
